Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.11,0:00:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,今天有要給野崎君的慰勞品
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.56,0:00:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,慰勞品?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.54,0:00:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.18,0:00:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你最近好像很累
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.09,0:00:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我帶了有治癒效果的音樂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.64,0:00:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,的確是很美妙的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.61,0:00:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.35,0:00:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.51,0:00:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,真不愧是「聲樂社的羅蕾萊」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.04,0:00:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那個是結月的歌聲喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.87,0:00:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,羅蕾萊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.64,0:00:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那是以美麗的歌聲誘惑船員
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.64,0:00:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,使其破滅的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.15,0:00:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.26,0:00:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.01,0:00:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,傳球
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.10,0:01:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,射籃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.98,0:01:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯? 若松
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.14,0:01:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 野崎學長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.33,0:01:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.99,0:01:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,射籃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.68,0:01:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你 你沒事吧? 若松
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.02,0:01:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:45.47,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)}あの子が昨日 なんかすごく優しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:45.47,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)}她昨天感覺非常溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.47,0:01:48.92,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an7}{\fad(300,500)}君じゃなきゃダメみたい
